{"tid":1909393,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"人大咗，覺得死亡都唔係最後歸宿","createTime":"2020-03-04T02:29:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-05T13:14:32.000Z","uid":138232,"like":23,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"23a36e334f89ea0ec4e2beafc82be0a54e61a5e2","tid":1909393,"uid":138232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T02:29:59.000Z","msg":"細個成日幻想<br />\n會有死後世界<br />\n可以重新嚟過<br />\n可以重新選擇<br />\n一定會做得更加好<br />\n想一死了知<br />\n離開呢個世界<br />\n斷絕所有關係<br />\n變成一個靈體<br />\n可以飛嚟飛去<br />\n應該會開心好多<br />\n但其實<br />\n再諗諗<br />\n如果真係有第二個世界<br />\n嗰邊都係會有其他人<br />\n有比我努力嘅人<br />\n有比我幸運嘅人<br />\n有比我富有嘅人<br />\n如果我一成不變<br />\n去到邊個世界<br />\n都只係垃圾<br />\n死唔死都冇分別<br />\n學校係咁<br />\n職場係咁<br />\n世界都係咁<br />\n心態比人弱<br />\n你用咩身份、咩形態<br />\n都係垃圾<br />\n永生永世<br />\n都係垃圾<br />\n呢個係現實<br />\n走唔甩<br />\n點都要面對<br />\n既然係咁<br />\n不如老老實實面對<br />\n壓力又好<br />\n困難都好<br />\n當係一種修練<br />\n或者係一種準備<br />\n至少<br />\n由倒數第二開始<br />\n慢慢行番上去<br />\n咁樣<br />\n或者<br />\n先會搵到自己嘅歸宿"},{"pid":"d5eff58610d3c7cbd362ec87474cf1a3baf4a345","tid":1909393,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T02:32:55.000Z","msg":"我明 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab26f86fa659c803de9b3106dca7322ca0bcbdbf","tid":1909393,"uid":9091,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T02:35:56.000Z","msg":"咪玩<br />\n想死嘅人根本唔在乎有冇死後世界<br />\n只係唔想再玩落去<br />\n<br />\nPs想死 不過怕痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d79ef734a74e1faefd49b30b62195f162150d110","tid":1909393,"uid":87670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T02:38:00.000Z","msg":"想努力咪努力"},{"pid":"bdba8d9f2e6c2865d4bd685cf490524eea52c026","tid":1909393,"uid":138232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab26f86fa659c803de9b3106dca7322ca0bcbdbf","tid":1909393,"uid":9091,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T02:35:56.000Z","msg":"咪玩<br />\n想死嘅人根本唔在乎有冇死後世界<br />\n只係唔想再玩落去<br />\n<br />\nPs想死 不過怕痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T02:42:20.000Z","msg":"你在唔在乎唔緊要<br />\n你嘅諗法重來冇人在乎<br />\n你生前比人蝦<br />\n你死咗都要比其他鬼繼續欺凌<br />\n你永遠都要玩<br />\n你只可以選擇做個努力嘅廢柴"},{"pid":"ac31dcc4be054e122986ba10b8e40328c8553670","tid":1909393,"uid":138232,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d79ef734a74e1faefd49b30b62195f162150d110","tid":1909393,"uid":87670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T02:38:00.000Z","msg":"想努力咪努力"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T02:43:52.000Z","msg":"咁啲心靈雞湯就唔洗咁貴<br />\n你唔需要<br />\n係你福氣"},{"pid":"ba31b912e00177d4021b37c339fd77f4645c3bae","tid":1909393,"uid":138232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5eff58610d3c7cbd362ec87474cf1a3baf4a345","tid":1909393,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T02:32:55.000Z","msg":"我明 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T02:44:23.000Z","msg":"堅持住"},{"pid":"91a245b668fc18dcf887957ebe8278e7dd0a3dcb","tid":1909393,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T03:02:05.000Z","msg":"變潮文未？"},{"pid":"a105a70fab1ea05acdbd68d89efa865015c0bb91","tid":1909393,"uid":138232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91a245b668fc18dcf887957ebe8278e7dd0a3dcb","tid":1909393,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T03:02:05.000Z","msg":"變潮文未？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T03:03:56.000Z","msg":"你鐘意就係"},{"pid":"3da3cebfff6c2864dd0e6ee5889a3000c784def5","tid":1909393,"uid":128600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T03:12:04.000Z","msg":"人類死咗會返去五維空間"},{"pid":"78b4949df9d89b1289d8bd3dbfe3dfe08378891a","tid":1909393,"uid":303133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T03:13:59.000Z","msg":"想努力咪努力 甘於做垃圾咪做垃圾"},{"pid":"c45f6ca612dd956693d5aa8467f2547039e2b00a","tid":1